---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Botox | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Botox softens wrinkles and lines with a safe, quick injectable treatment for natural-looking results.", "canonical": "/services/botox", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{
    --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8;
  }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
  .faq-toggle{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; margin-right:.5rem; flex:0 0 auto; }
  details.faq[open] .plus{ display:none; }
  details.faq:not([open]) .minus{ display:none; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
</style>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] font-semibold tracking-tight">Botox</h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-[1.125rem] md:text-xl muted measure">Botox injections temporarily relax specific facial muscles to soften wrinkles and lines, providing a refreshed and natural look.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 h-px w-full border-t rule"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">

      <!-- DESCRIPTION -->
      <section id="description" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Description</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 muted dropcap">
          Botox is a cosmetic injectable treatment using purified Botulinum toxin type A to temporarily relax targeted muscles. By blocking nerve signals, Botox smooths dynamic wrinkles like frown lines, forehead creases, and crow’s feet. Results appear within days and last 3–4 months on average, with regular treatments maintaining a youthful, refreshed look.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 muted">
          This treatment is non-surgical, quick, and safe when performed by trained providers. Botox is designed for natural-looking results — refreshing your appearance without freezing your expression.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 ataglance">
          <span>FDA-approved</span>
          <span>3–4 months duration</span>
          <span>Non-surgical</span>
          <span>Natural-looking results</span>
        </div>
        <p class="pullquote">“A refreshed look, not a frozen one.”</p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- BENEFITS -->
      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2>
        <ul class="mt-3 muted list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Reduces fine lines and wrinkles by relaxing muscles.</li>
          <li>Helps prevent deeper lines from forming with repeated use.</li>
          <li>Quick treatment with no downtime, ideal for busy schedules.</li>
          <li>Delivers subtle, natural-looking rejuvenation.</li>
          <li>Well-established safety record when performed by professionals.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PROCESS -->
      <section id="process" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 timeline space-y-6">
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">1</div><p class="tl-title">Consultation</p><p class="muted mt-1">Review goals, facial movements, and medical history. Injection sites are mapped for precision.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">2</div><p class="tl-title">Treatment</p><p class="muted mt-1">Small amounts of Botox are injected into targeted muscles with minimal discomfort.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">3</div><p class="tl-title">Follow-Up</p><p class="muted mt-1">Results appear in 3–7 days with peak effect by 2 weeks. Touch-ups may be offered if needed.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PRE & POST -->
      <section id="care" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div><p class="font-medium">Before your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li>Avoid blood-thinning medications and alcohol for 24 hours.</li>
              <li>Reschedule if you are ill or have an active infection.</li>
              <li>Arrive with a clean face; avoid heavy skincare or makeup.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div><p class="font-medium">After your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li>Do not rub or press the treated areas for 12 hours.</li>
              <li>Stay upright for 3–4 hours after injections.</li>
              <li>Avoid strenuous exercise and heat for 24 hours.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- FAQS -->
      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How soon will I see results?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Most patients notice results in 3–4 days, with full effect within 10–14 days.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How long do results last?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Results typically last 3–4 months before muscle activity gradually returns.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Will I look frozen?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">No. When done correctly, Botox smooths wrinkles while allowing natural expression.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Are there side effects?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Side effects are uncommon and usually mild, such as slight redness, swelling, or bruising at injection sites.</p></details>
        </div>
      </section>

    </article>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
